# IIoT Data Pipeline & Machine Analysis

## Run locally (Python)

1. Create and activate a virtual environment

```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
```

2. Install dependencies

```powershell
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Initialize the QuestDB schema (required once)

```powershell
python src/consumer/init_db.py
```

4. Start the simulator (publishes MQTT messages)

```powershell
python src/simulator/machine_simulator.py
```

5. Start the consumer (stores messages to QuestDB)

```powershell
python src/consumer/mqtt_consumer.py
```

---

## Run with Docker (recommended)

1. Build and start all services:

```powershell
docker compose up --build
```

2. Open QuestDB web console:

- http://localhost:9000

3. Open the Analytics API docs:

- http://localhost:8000/docs

---